description:
Homes England is seeking to appoint a member of the property professional services framework to assist in the procurement of a member of the Delivery Partner Panel (DPP3) to enable the disposal of East Quayside, Newcastle in line with sites planning brief.

The scope of services will involve:

(i)	Delivery Assessment/Market Commentary;
(ii)	Review Invitation to Tender (ITT);
(iii)	Evaluation of bidder responses;
(iv)	Recommendation report;
(v)	Franking valuation.

